       "=== Document 10 ===\n",
       "Source: blog\n",
       "with batch size = 1: \n",
       "\n",
       "|quantization |act_order|bits|group_size|kernel|Load time (s)|Per-token latency (ms)|Throughput (tok/s)|Peak memory\n",
